Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類一直在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與來自神秘遠方的敵人 － {\fnArial}Festum{\fnsimhei} 戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你死就是我亡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.96,0:00:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此毫無妥協的餘地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.39,0:01:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護一些人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一些人犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一個講述無休止的戰爭中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:01:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存者的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.33,0:02:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7月20日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:47.26,pic1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(551,425)\frz-20}（歡慶畢業）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉行了那一年的第二個「畢業」典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…今與諸位學長分別
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人深感惆悵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們絕不會忘記諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請學長們一切珍重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勿忘島上渡過的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衷心祝願身體健康 工作順利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謹表贈別之意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭賀諸位畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有學生會長氣勢的告別辭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 副會長幫我想的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道 你這懶蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要和你分別了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空會回來看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「畢業」成了定局之後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有些不適應 對這座島
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘快融入大人之中反而更輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也早點確定自己的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁還能活在義務教育世界裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:04:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如向喜歡的人告白之類的 什麼都行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心存遺憾是最糟糕的 肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有留下遺憾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 僚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義務教育都沒完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就進入完全不同的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是龍宮島特有的光景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎和劍司一如既往的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還賭劍司贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士賭哪邊贏？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶一提劍司是13連敗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去可是很要好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎和總士 他們倆小時候常在一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在一起玩是有原因的吧 相互之間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸 佑未
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事要低頭懇求身為副會長的你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我「畢業」了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我養著它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！帶它一起走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 果然是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我有事先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 僚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將陵學長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 藏前 接下來的事拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將陵學長竟然先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他知道明天有休學典禮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不想說是去醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天他能撐著來就已經很辛苦了 一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 那傢伙是個懶蟲也是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們加油幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的 只是有些貧血
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你還挺熱心腸的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為看你表情很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎沒跟其他人一起回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別老等著劍司那樣的人沖到面前來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要主動和別人搞好關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說你幫了我 說這話好像不大厚道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 果然是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧有你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去遠見醫生那邊喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了 我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐間也來作檢查？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚睡覺之前還好好的 今天卻不能上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是遺傳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將陵學長得的病跟媽媽一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然和媽媽沒有血緣關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我很羡慕羽佐間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.81,0:07:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.11,0:07:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有位真心體貼你的好母親
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,症狀穩定下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,減少止疼藥的劑量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.87,0:08:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 無法再復原了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,症狀也有可能完全消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說那個選拔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僚 情況一定不會悲觀的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 聽說可以自願參加 松了口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最害怕一事無成就結束了生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母親去世已經兩年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨立生活有困難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島這麼小 總有人幫我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 我也不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐間 不回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢馬上就回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 有個好朋友真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的好朋友一半以上都「畢業」了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將陵學長真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅持上學 還當學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在我休假時 大家擅自決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自決定？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 一上學就突然多了個頭銜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然這樣 不覺得討厭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像硬塞給你似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家沒有忘記我 很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們為我準備了容身之處 我應該報恩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.91,0:09:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.29,0:09:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算去學校 恐怕也沒有容身之處了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍惜陪在你身邊的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校長 真壁叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.95,0:10:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 生駒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我馬上去沏茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 只是來打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走了 生駒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心養病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 今天上午又舉行「畢業」典禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.82,0:10:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放暑假之前 舉行好幾次「畢業」典禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.73,0:10:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裏是個荒僻的小島吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸小時候的畢業典禮也是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我「畢業」後會去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…會陪在爸爸身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連母親的份一起…直到永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪兒也不去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所羅門重複發出反應
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預計700小時之內將得到明確應答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不能迎擊敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島上的核正在形成人格 若此時和敵人接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整座島都被奪取的可能性太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是只能將防禦系統降低到極限嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們直接跟生駒談了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重點將全部{\fnArial}Fafner{\r}相關兵器嚴密封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為將被敵人奪取後的打擊降到最低限度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能主動封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 僅此實在不能算是萬全之策
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對此生駒所提出回避危機的計畫 即是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}計畫？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若要實施 {\fnArial}TSX{\fnsimhei}的投入是大前提
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 難道要讓孩子們參與嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:12:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要掌控這個島的人們共同決斷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（暑假）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要打贏你 別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑未學姐是主動競選進學生會的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得很忙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個若無其事帶狗來學校還遊手好閒的學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…只是覺得好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是副會長的工作 還是學生會長？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢…說不定兩個都是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.69,0:13:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天要和朋友出去一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友約我去海邊玩 很快就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒讓我想起這島雖小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候卻也不愁找不到地方玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你約我來的 自己卻不下去遊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你的泳姿 就失去信心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 你去看過遠見醫生了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 只是有些不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微能明白這樣的人的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一直和爸爸生活在一起 習慣照顧人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體也曬暖了 去遊一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒想過讓別人照顧我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果傷了你的心 我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.19,0:14:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天很開心 許久未曾這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至能稍微拋開爸爸的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.21,0:15:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Al…vis…{\fnsimhei}必須…得去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去{\fnArial}Alvis…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:15:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:15:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑未
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士同學 令尊常去看我父親
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 說是在公事上聽取一些建議
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnsimhei}嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Plan…L
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}計畫？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Fafner…Titan-model
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnsimhei}是為了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嗎 你在那裏嗎 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,識別限制編碼確認為第三級
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這些…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}TSX
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}TS…X
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Fafner Titan-model
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們唯一的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝賀你「畢業」 佑未
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的聲音一直在我腦海裏迴響
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,催眠學習({\fnArial}Memorizing{\fnsimhei})的知識\N是作為聲音來被認知的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到的是媽媽的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.99,0:19:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,催眠學習？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小開始就被無意識灌輸的各種知識
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現今的世界形勢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在於島內部的{\fnArial}Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及與敵人戰鬥的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnsimhei}的人就算「畢業」了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦知道 就無法回到平常的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.49,0:19:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要選擇和大人們一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僚為什麼沒有離開島
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親所設立的拯救島的L計畫啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都不瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對父親的事情一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親一定想讓我參加這個計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會念著{\fnArial}Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 你還什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就一直都明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.47,0:20:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.18,0:20:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑未
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒跟你出去 爸爸就不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.13,0:20:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 將陵學長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.75,0:20:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好，普庫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定……要「畢業」了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.25,0:20:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假結束後就離開島 和大人們一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:21:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將陵學長真厲害 我就不敢想什麼工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.00,0:21:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到的事 羽佐間也一定能做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我不在了 也請至少記住這些話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要選擇和父親相同的道路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求您成全
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.97,0:21:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的指令書
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何也要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.99,0:21:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下終於可以報答給我容身之處的人們了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定要「畢業」了 來打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要「畢業」了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.90,0:21:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了參加父親的計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:21:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛和校長先生談過了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 這要面對面和敵人打仗的！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣 我聽說此前已經進行過許多次這樣的計畫了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.00,0:22:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且無人生還
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次也一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.05,0:22:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你又為什麼要參加呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.70,0:22:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問你…為什麼要約我去海邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.85,0:22:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.80,0:22:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算瞞著我一個人消失嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.90,0:22:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去！別再靠近我！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 選拔成員聚齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠自主催眠學習
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.86,0:22:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,協同線路產生數值高的最適合者們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:22:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑未
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.58,0:23:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是今天起負責各位訓練的日野惠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.62,0:23:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想退出作戰的人可隨時向我提出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.94,0:23:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼開始說明{\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}計畫的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnsimhei}的全貌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.39,0:23:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在敵人正逐漸察覺此島的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.66,0:23:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}計畫正是為了避免之
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.93,0:23:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}即指{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnsimhei}的左翼 {\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}區域
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.68,0:23:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其從島上分離開 成為{\fnArial}L Boat
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.24,0:23:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}L Boat{\fnsimhei}能夠在超越敵人探知能力的深海中前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到島的防禦圈外上浮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸引敵人 按既定航線繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為期兩個月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.20,0:23:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓其誤以為{\fnArial}L Boat{\fnsimhei}就是龍宮島
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.83,0:23:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須持續迎擊敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.17,0:23:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘{\fnArial}L Boat{\fnsimhei}是自動駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.80,0:23:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連自己身在何處也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.03,0:23:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這將是極其嚴苛的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.17,0:23:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想退出的人請提出
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.68,0:24:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼立即開始訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.46,0:24:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}的第一大特徵 即無需操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.49,0:24:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要遵從催眠學習獲得的知識 和{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}一體化
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.10,0:24:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受精神的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.53,0:24:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是訓練用的虛擬現實
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.50,0:24:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請自由活動
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.21,0:24:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.77,0:24:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.56,0:24:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.25,0:24:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能跑 這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.09,0:24:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸毫無困難
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.71,0:24:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼 這不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.55,0:24:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.05,0:24:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二大特徵 即各機內置系統間的交叉({\fnArial}Crossing{\fnsimhei})
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.51,0:24:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共用思考 防止被敵人讀取
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.84,0:25:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要接受同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.60,0:25:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.55,0:25:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僚 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.16,0:25:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.05,0:25:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 請換其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.94,0:25:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了取得平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.88,0:25:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是他 你馬上就能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.02,0:25:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.01,0:25:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.05,0:25:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑未 你害怕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.53,0:25:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是僚的感覺？你在享受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.33,0:25:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上這個 我也能游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.72,0:25:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限制時間到 請離開駕駛艙
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.99,0:25:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}的第三大特徵
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.14,0:25:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即駕駛員會被同化現象所侵擾
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.32,0:25:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘坐次數越多 肉體越容易發生異常
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.02,0:25:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最壞情況下可能危及生命
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.78,0:25:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退出吧 佑未
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.44,0:26:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹不了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.43,0:26:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了爸爸一定要讓計畫成功
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.92,0:26:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是一開始就不想活著回去的人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.20,0:26:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如退出算了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.48,0:26:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選拔成員共8人 無人退出
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.33,0:26:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}共4架 每架由兩人交替駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.31,0:26:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次戰鬥時間15分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.41,0:26:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人交替 各戰鬥450秒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.94,0:26:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷重複的戰鬥訓練 以及敵人的確認
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.80,0:26:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矽狀生命體 － {\fnArial}Festum {\fnsimhei}即敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.65,0:26:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有統一的思考 能適應任何環境
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.00,0:26:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但未曾在海中發現過
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.81,0:26:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據推測是其若與海中結晶物同化
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.82,0:26:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會成為不規則塊狀物
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.98,0:26:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是「畢業」的準備工作
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.88,0:26:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而對我來說 還有一項重要的準備工作
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.07,0:27:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 普庫 很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.46,0:27:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我給的 它從不吃任何食物
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.02,0:27:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定察覺到會被丟下了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.21,0:27:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能帶狗一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.25,0:27:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為飼主 要負起責任
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.43,0:27:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條狗是從前媽媽帶回來 讓我當成朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.68,0:27:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法去上學時
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.50,0:27:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有它在身邊 我就不會感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.20,0:27:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.30,0:27:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明知有毒還去吃的對吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.30,0:27:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.00,0:27:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝婆婆 我下次再來
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.81,0:28:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.05,0:28:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖等著學長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.28,0:28:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為獎勵 學長們的慰問品分你一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.28,0:28:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在Nothung model正在啟動測試中
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.49,0:28:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的新型{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.48,0:28:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.36,0:28:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個月後計畫完畢之前 應該趕得上
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.74,0:28:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們沒事 就能來迎接我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.26,0:28:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.03,0:28:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將陵學長 它好像肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.88,0:28:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.60,0:28:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這是隨身物品 可能有點重
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.12,0:28:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.92,0:28:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.87,0:28:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我會把它當成學長好好珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.74,0:28:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.75,0:28:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是做好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.84,0:28:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.02,0:28:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 完成最後一項準備時
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.44,0:28:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為何想起了佑未的話
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.52,0:29:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就覺得回不去的人 應該退出
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.03,0:29:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑未這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.28,0:29:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 多半佑未是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.87,0:29:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偽裝鏡面 維持{\fnArial}ROM{\fnsimhei}模式
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.94,0:29:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接續區域 全部隔離壁以緊急模式封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.88,0:29:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全隔離壁封鎖確認
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.60,0:29:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開啟注水閥
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.26,0:29:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接續區域 確認注水
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.72,0:29:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}L Boat{\fnsimhei}艦橋呼叫{\fnArial}CDC
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.96,0:29:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,程式鏈結無異常
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.77,0:29:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注水完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.90,0:29:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}L Boat {\fnsimhei}出發準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.86,0:29:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}區域分離準備 全部完成
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.60,0:29:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分離
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.99,0:29:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}L Boat{\fnsimhei}控制程式開始運行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.81,0:29:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駛向波盾圈外
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.81,0:29:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個月後再會
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.53,0:29:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝他們好運
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.86,0:29:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二步驟啟動 作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.99,0:29:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.62,0:30:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離計畫結束的時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.76,0:30:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9月2號 {\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}計畫啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.04,0:30:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}L{\fnsimhei}即{\fnArial}Left {\fnsimhei}左邊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.43,0:30:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也含有離去的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.45,0:30:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如這個詞所說 我們離開了島
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.20,0:30:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發後第3天 我們的小島上浮了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.85,0:30:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起 這裏就是龍宮島了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.40,0:30:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人實體化 是{\fnArial}Sphinx {\fnsimhei}型
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.63,0:30:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以普通武器牽制 {\fnArial}Fafner {\fnsimhei}準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.45,0:30:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}能量傳輸線連接
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.84,0:30:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}7至8號
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.31,0:30:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}Brunhild{\fnsimhei}系統啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.75,0:30:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}資料線確認
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.70,0:30:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}搭乘輸入優先
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.76,0:30:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}速度控制
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.89,0:30:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}負極資料登錄中
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.14,0:30:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}誤差修正
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.92,0:30:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}感測器開放
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.92,0:30:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}各機正常
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.25,0:30:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}封鎖解除
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.77,0:30:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}Niebelungen{\fnsimhei}系統開啟確認
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.53,0:30:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}Siegfried{\fnsimhei}系統接續完成
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.87,0:30:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}接續杆連接
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.06,0:30:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}艙門開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.41,0:30:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}啟動升降架接續
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.17,0:30:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}上升
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.27,0:31:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}潮流資料 環境資料及氣象資料登錄完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.23,0:31:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次見到的敵人 超乎想像的美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.82,0:31:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑未 打倒他們
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.86,0:31:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.77,0:32:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 打倒敵人了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.41,0:32:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次打倒敵人 大家深受鼓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.03,0:32:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試圖用興奮壓抑不安
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.59,0:32:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有歸路了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.60,0:32:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 為什麼你會吃我喂的麵包？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.30,0:32:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也和你一樣是被人收養的 被皆城家…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.20,0:32:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏…是以前
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.50,0:32:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fafner的啟動實驗失敗所產生的空洞
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.80,0:33:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 聽說因為同化現象 全都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.60,0:33:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍有不慎 就會被虛無吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.10,0:33:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也不怕嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.50,0:33:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 和將陵學長所面對的相比…那些根本不足為懼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.78,0:33:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我想像的小
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.38,0:33:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有內置{\fnArial}Siegfried{\fnsimhei}系統
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.37,0:33:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.86,0:33:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.51,0:33:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時可以
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.86,0:33:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Markeins {\fnsimhei}終止啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.11,0:33:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs20}{\fnArial}eins:{\fnsimhei}德語「1」
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.79,0:33:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然對與{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}一體化來說 是致命傷
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.55,0:33:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次 請讓我再試一次
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.14,0:33:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行 動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.24,0:33:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.62,0:34:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員喪失意識了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.88,0:34:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3號機的駕駛員來這邊 交換
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.97,0:34:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.06,0:34:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩天一次 敵人不斷來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.20,0:34:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後有人犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.54,0:34:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第6次戰鬥時 那件事發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.19,0:34:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是乘坐{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.16,0:34:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員的肉體越會結晶化
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.70,0:34:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同化現象
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.59,0:34:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第8次戰鬥時 又有一人倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.52,0:34:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.04,0:35:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是敵人 而是本應是武器的{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.74,0:35:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為減少駕駛員的消耗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.55,0:35:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該把戰鬥時間從15分鐘縮短為10分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.08,0:35:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣出擊次數就會增大
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.64,0:35:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊時 牽制敵人的彈藥不足
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.30,0:35:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反需要增加戰鬥時間
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.68,0:35:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.11,0:35:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生駒
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.31,0:35:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從父親口中聽說過這個計畫的內容嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.73,0:35:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.02,0:35:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計畫結束時的逃生方法是什麼 連我也未被告知
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.88,0:35:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便沒有逃生方法 我也早有心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.01,0:35:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…父親他 絕不會把我們當成犧牲品
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.88,0:35:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑未的父親並不笨
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.21,0:35:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不可能提出這麼快就無法戰鬥的計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.64,0:35:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該縮短戰鬥時間到10分鐘 減少駕駛員的消耗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.90,0:36:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與根據現狀的判斷相比 你更相信計畫立案者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.09,0:36:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑未的父親自己也打算參加
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.27,0:36:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為他想活著回島
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.51,0:36:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說重病纏身時日無多的人還打算生還嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.16,0:36:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.18,0:36:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.84,0:36:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知從何時起 我就變得如此相信
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.78,0:36:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有理由
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.35,0:36:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是覺得 如果自己病情嚴重惡化
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.39,0:36:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會比現在更想活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.88,0:36:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人在放哨？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.02,0:36:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.39,0:36:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.63,0:36:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.14,0:36:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 在擔心我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.94,0:36:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.37,0:36:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太擔心的話 你又要發火了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.06,0:36:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候被人提起自己的身體 有些害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.90,0:36:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天謝謝你 替我父親辯護
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.27,0:36:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是辯護
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.31,0:37:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是…對不起 你父親的事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.44,0:37:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為無法活著回去也無所謂的 是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.89,0:37:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 你一直想消失
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.06,0:37:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺你和爸爸一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.47,0:37:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是唯有你 我不想失去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.35,0:37:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快到會議室來
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.24,0:37:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.41,0:37:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封閉的區域自動開啟了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.98,0:37:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是給我們的補給
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.97,0:37:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.55,0:37:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人會讀取我們的思考
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.05,0:37:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判斷武器的能力而進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.84,0:37:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要騙過敵人先得騙過自己 對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.49,0:37:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.49,0:37:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎在一定時期後 就會提供一些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.63,0:38:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而最後打開的…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.67,0:38:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是逃生的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.62,0:38:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 勿庸置疑
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.14,0:38:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸果然了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.62,0:38:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想要的一定是生存之地 而不是葬身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.54,0:38:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.84,0:38:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員另選其他人擔任
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.49,0:38:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來操縱{\fnArial}Siegfried{\fnsimhei}系統 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.63,0:38:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您叫我不親臨陣前 反而把同伴送去戰場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.63,0:38:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這比較適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.14,0:38:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親認為這次計畫能有多少人生還
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.79,0:38:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生駒提出的生存率極低
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.84,0:38:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但您依然批准了計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.17,0:38:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要我做同樣的事 為了保護島而付出犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.90,0:38:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生駒想盡力生存下來
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.01,0:39:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我批准了計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.58,0:39:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我堅信他們能夠全部生還
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.39,0:39:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在殘酷的境遇中掙扎求生者的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.76,0:39:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能夠背負嗎 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.40,0:39:23.10,pic2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(473,201)}（活下去）
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.41,0:39:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥越來越激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.68,0:39:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑未
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.73,0:40:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我動啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.09,0:40:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.15,0:40:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅有的4架{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}中 有一架喪失了機能
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.51,0:40:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員的數量再次減少
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.70,0:40:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尚能戰鬥的人身上 也出現了同化現象的早期症狀
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.02,0:40:32.53,pic3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（希望早日結束）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.85,0:40:33.53,pic4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（快點！快點！快點！我想回家！）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.71,0:40:34.43,pic5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（爸爸 媽媽）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.57,0:40:35.20,pic6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我們在這裏）
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.82,0:40:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 終於駕駛員中也開始出現犧牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.62,0:40:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸弘
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.55,0:41:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是同化現象的末期症狀
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.80,0:41:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴們 一個接一個 在我們眼前消失
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.51,0:41:19.97,pic7,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（反正大家最後都要死）
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.14,0:41:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 為什麼寫這個
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.90,0:41:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說啊 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.00,0:41:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.84,0:41:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再逼他了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.91,0:41:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人的心中都充滿了恐懼 憤怒和悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.65,0:41:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩下兩周
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.40,0:41:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 我們再度失去了{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}和駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.29,0:42:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同化現象的早期症狀嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.54,0:42:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.78,0:42:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧這個 才不會被其他人發現
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.52,0:42:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說在第三次啟動時成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.85,0:42:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣身體就出現異變 真丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.80,0:42:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將陵學長他們還要更加辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.22,0:42:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一派和平
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.99,0:42:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想把學長們的事告訴他們
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.03,0:42:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會讓學長們的戰鬥變得毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.95,0:42:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人做出犧牲 卻只有我們待在安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.18,0:42:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣正確嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.37,0:42:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能祈求這是正確的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.26,0:42:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說皆城已經決定操縱系統了？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.10,0:42:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.73,0:42:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倖存下來的有兩架{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.77,0:42:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3名駕駛員和8位成人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.52,0:43:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.73,0:43:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏竟然有通道
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.12,0:43:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是逃生方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.28,0:43:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.31,0:43:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.25,0:43:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑未
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.08,0:43:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了嗎 那艘潛水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.91,0:43:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠搭乘40人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.78,0:43:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸認為所有人都能生還
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.93,0:43:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.41,0:43:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經活到現在了 一定要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.93,0:43:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}第9至第17區域注水開始
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.65,0:43:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}第1第2第3隔離壁開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.08,0:43:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}逃生程式確認
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.79,0:43:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}L Boat Fenrir{\fnsimhei}啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.06,0:43:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想與{\fnArial}Festum{\fnsimhei}同歸於盡 銷毀這個島嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.07,0:43:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑未
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.53,0:43:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.97,0:44:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}L Boat Fenrir{\fnsimhei}釋放還有5秒
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.75,0:44:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.71,0:44:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.66,0:44:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.53,0:44:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.40,0:44:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防禦圈內有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.31,0:44:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是潛水艇和{\fnArial}Titan-model
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.16,0:44:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備出擊 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.37,0:44:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Fafner Markzwei {\fnsimhei}出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.91,0:44:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs20}{\fnArial}zwei:{\fnsimhei}德語「2」
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.25,0:44:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等著 我一定會帶他回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.06,0:44:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中間正面出現{\fnArial}Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.95,0:44:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短魚雷及導彈戰準備
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.02,0:44:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,252度也出現敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.47,0:44:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.46,0:45:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.27,0:45:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後方約20公里處
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.43,0:45:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.42,0:45:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們幾時能下水了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.46,0:45:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛水艇消失
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.86,0:45:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.65,0:45:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島應該在這個方向 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.16,0:45:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 佑未
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.14,0:45:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能過去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.25,0:45:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是已經知道龍宮島在這前面了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.15,0:45:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.81,0:45:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能百分之百確定 就不能這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.80,0:45:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易活到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.17,0:45:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回去 回島上去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.55,0:45:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況已經變了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.01,0:45:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能讓大家的戰鬥失去意義
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.70,0:45:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 在有人來迎接我們之前
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.20,0:45:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長 拜託你…不要死 
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.71,0:45:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Titan-model{\fnsimhei}開始移動
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.08,0:45:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠離島嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.13,0:46:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士 停住{\fnArial}Markzwei
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.49,0:46:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能發生了最壞的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.10,0:46:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.59,0:46:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓整座島置身險境 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.49,0:46:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Markzwei {\fnsimhei}停止前進
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.63,0:46:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 不去接學長他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.26,0:46:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原地待機 {\fnArial}Markzwei
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.88,0:46:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況變了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.09,0:46:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀 不是要去接學長他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.06,0:46:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.68,0:46:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原地待機！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.10,0:46:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我絕不認同
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.55,0:46:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖定{\fnArial}Markzwei{\fnsimhei}的操作
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.35,0:46:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你讓我去 皆城 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.25,0:46:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城 聽得見吧 為什麼不說話
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.82,0:46:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 皆城 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.96,0:46:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.35,0:46:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}CDC {\fnsimhei}那邊是有著實戰經驗的機體和駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.72,0:46:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能回收那些資料
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.57,0:47:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的戰力將大幅提升
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.24,0:47:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也更能抵抗敵人的入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.13,0:47:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.16,0:47:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得與敵人戰鬥力量的絕好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.16,0:47:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您打算眼睜睜地錯過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.25,0:47:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}是做什麼用的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.47,0:47:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.71,0:47:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不能讓{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnsimhei}離開防禦圈
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.60,0:47:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.40,0:47:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Markzwei {\fnsimhei}重整機體
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.06,0:47:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後全力追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.02,0:47:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.67,0:47:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計測目標週邊所有振動
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.00,0:47:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.63,0:47:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就能得到答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.18,0:47:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潮流的資料收集到了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.39,0:47:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在這裏運氣好的話
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.43,0:47:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少殘骸能回到島上
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.30,0:47:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.66,0:47:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.18,0:48:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 制止了我
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.15,0:48:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 佑未
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.30,0:48:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.09,0:48:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.63,0:48:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我一直喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.88,0:48:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能 從很久之前
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.83,0:48:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道是不是喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.78,0:48:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知何時 已經超越了那種感情
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.05,0:48:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.11,0:48:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.22,0:48:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島上的人們會知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.78,0:48:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.29,0:48:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸會稱讚我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.44,0:49:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪？下在海底？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.90,0:49:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海雪
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.90,0:49:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}海雪：海底浮游生物組成的絮狀物 看起來像雪
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.81,0:49:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在稱讚我們呢 一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.87,0:49:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.54,0:49:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在陪在我身邊的是你 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.57,0:49:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.18,0:49:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.03,0:49:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.47,0:49:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好像還有更多更深的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.60,0:49:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你陪在身邊 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.54,0:50:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑未
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.00,0:50:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 佑未
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.70,0:50:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了嗎 佑未
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.23,0:50:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上就是我們的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.93,0:50:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈禱有人能聽到這些
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.56,0:50:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你們以前從未到過海中
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.70,0:50:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由於無法代謝而結晶化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.68,0:51:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代謝…就是使身體重生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.42,0:51:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也掌握了這些
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.13,0:51:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 才擁有了生命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.37,0:51:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Fenrir{\fnsimhei}釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.54,0:51:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認信源地
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.26,0:51:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判斷為海底有人啟動了{\fnArial}Fenrir
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.11,0:51:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.71,0:51:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心機體被敵人同化
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.56,0:51:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這說明海底也存在{\fnArial}Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.69,0:51:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是給我們的資訊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.86,0:51:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Markzwei 返航
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.46,0:51:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏已經 沒有任何人了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.90,0:52:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是第一波盾的潮流感應器探查到的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.14,0:52:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著珍貴的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.89,0:52:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.98,0:52:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 分析了潮流後才啟動的{\fnArial}Fenrir
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.33,0:52:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是保持鎮靜直到最後的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.85,0:52:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰駕駛的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.36,0:52:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據調查 似乎只留下了音頻記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.68,0:52:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 普庫 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.32,0:52:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.27,0:52:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上就是我們的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.30,0:53:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈禱有人能聽到這些
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.19,0:53:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普庫
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.10,0:53:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 待在這裏的是將陵學長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.74,0:53:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是陪伴佑未學姐直到最後的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.74,0:54:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起 一定是去了將陵學長身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.37,0:54:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回去了 想把它送回龍宮島
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.17,0:54:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所羅門的反應顯示著徵兆
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.77,0:54:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預計很快將輪到{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnsimhei}迎擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.83,0:54:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平僅僅維持了半年
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.30,0:54:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將陵學長他們的戰鬥 只有這點意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.77,0:54:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直享受著別人贏來並讓給的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.67,0:54:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便那和平只有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.96,0:54:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會感謝其價值
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.28,0:54:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.32,0:54:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待與你並肩作戰的時刻到來
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.93,0:55:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 我們繼承了和平與戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.82,0:55:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們想要活下去的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.18,0:55:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及在前線戰鬥者的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.42,0:55:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能否全部承受呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.88,0:55:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不斷重複問著自己
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.91,0:55:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案 就在今後的戰鬥中
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.51,0:55:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我們的戰鬥中
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.49,0:52:28.02,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どれくらい時間があれば
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.80,0:52:32.68,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心は繋がるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.92,0:52:39.46,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どこか寂しげな笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.82,0:52:43.92,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,癒せたらいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.54,0:52:51.95,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近すぎて気づけなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.76,0:52:57.11,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一番大事な人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.72,0:53:03.49,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍に居てくれるだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.80,0:53:09.16,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸せを感じられる
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.36,0:53:12.24,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲しみの夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.31,0:53:15.24,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜びの朝も
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.31,0:53:21.27,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あたしを見守ってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.78,0:53:27.43,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ただ一言「ありがとう」
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.77,0:53:32.76,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伝えられないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.25,0:53:36.16,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素直になるのが
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.29,0:53:39.12,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少し怖かった
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.33,0:53:44.74,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今あなたの腕の中
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.84,0:53:51.74,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心がほどけてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.98,0:54:00.94,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温かい安らぎに抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.49,0:54:15.95,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静けさにふと窓の外
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.81,0:54:20.72,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪が舞い降りている
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.81,0:54:27.10,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白に染まる世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.86,0:54:33.08,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたの音に寄り添う
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.36,0:54:36.16,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素直になるのが
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.30,0:54:39.23,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少し怖かった
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.40,0:54:44.75,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今あなたの腕の中
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.84,0:54:51.71,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心がほどけてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.10,0:55:02.27,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温かい安らぎに抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.49,0:52:28.02,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要經過多少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.80,0:52:32.68,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心才能相映
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.92,0:52:39.46,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,些許寂寞的笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.82,0:52:43.92,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多想將其治癒
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.54,0:52:51.95,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過靠近而未曾察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.76,0:52:57.11,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.72,0:53:03.49,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是陪在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.80,0:53:09.16,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.36,0:53:12.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.31,0:53:15.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜悅的清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.31,0:53:21.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都為我守候
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.78,0:53:27.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連一句感謝的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.77,0:53:32.76,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也未能傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.25,0:53:36.16,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要變得率直
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.29,0:53:39.12,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有些膽怯
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.33,0:53:44.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今在你懷中
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.84,0:53:51.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心漸漸釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.98,0:54:00.94,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被溫暖平靜擁抱
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.49,0:54:15.95,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗外靜靜地
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.81,0:54:20.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飄起了雪
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.81,0:54:27.10,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在純白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.86,0:54:33.08,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依偎著你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.36,0:54:36.16,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要變得率直
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.30,0:54:39.23,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有些膽怯
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.40,0:54:44.75,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今在你懷中
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.84,0:54:51.71,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心漸漸釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.10,0:55:02.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被溫暖平靜擁抱
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.67,0:39:36.32,im,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まぼろし移りよく季節
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.58,0:39:42.28,im,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思い出す幼き日
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.62,0:39:48.50,im,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戻れる場所が在ることを
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.74,0:39:53.95,im,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あたり前のように思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.13,0:40:06.84,im,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な瞳の奧から
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.05,0:40:12.82,im,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深い闇が導く
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.09,0:40:19.09,im,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦しむ為に生まれたの
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.29,0:40:24.04,im,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人はみな孤独抱える
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.60,0:40:31.21,im,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時に過去は重き足かせ
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.60,0:40:37.40,im,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今以上を望めなくするけど
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.25,0:40:43.47,im,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動き始めた歯車を
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.24,0:40:49.34,im,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,止めることは出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.49,0:40:55.48,im,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ためらい どれくらい 僕を試しますか
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.69,0:41:01.12,im,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小さく輝いてた 夢遙か
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.33,0:41:07.82,im,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戻りたい場所があれば戦える と
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.50,0:41:17.09,im,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呟いた声は 誰かに屆くだろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.67,0:39:36.32,imc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻夢般流轉的季節
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.58,0:39:42.28,imc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶中孩提時代
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.62,0:39:48.50,imc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有歸處在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.74,0:39:53.95,imc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,視之理所當然
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.13,0:40:06.84,imc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真的瞳眸深處
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.05,0:40:12.82,imc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在深淵中指引
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.09,0:40:19.09,imc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否為痛苦而生
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.29,0:40:24.04,imc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們滿懷孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.60,0:40:31.21,imc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去常是沉重的枷鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.60,0:40:37.40,imc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使現已不再苛求
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.25,0:40:43.47,imc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始轉動的齒輪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.24,0:40:49.34,imc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已無法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.49,0:40:55.48,imc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷惘還要考驗我多久
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.69,0:41:01.12,imc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃爍的夢想那般遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.33,0:41:07.82,imc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若為了歸處而戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.50,0:41:17.09,imc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呢喃的話語誰能聽見
